        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 6 at 6:28AM EDT by NWS Detroit/Pontiac MI</headline>
        <description>WEATHER...

* Patchy fog will impact southeastern Michigan during the morning
commute.

IMPACTS...

* Patchy dense fog may reduce visibilities to near zero at times.
</description>
        <instruction>* Patchy dense fog means areal coverage or duration of the
dense fog will be limited. Motorists are urged to use caution
and account for variable driving conditions by slowing down
and allowing extra time.

* Prepare, plan and stay informed. Visit http://go.usa.gov/c7kkP</instruction>
